We also want to calculate percent changes because this is the metric that well be using to visualize changes in the other scenarios, which dont have a common unburned reference value like burn severity. First, well need to calculate % differences, then well create equivalent plots to those above. Well use a standardized percent change calculation of Percent Change: ( Burn - Original ) / Original * 100
